description:
Darkness Radio presents A Dark & Stormy Night with guests Stormy Daniels & Justin Loupe

Dave Schrader is joined by paranormal investigators and experiencers, Stormy Daniels and Justin Loupe to discuss their foray into ghost hunting, personal experiences, the unique way and tools they use to explore claims of the supernatural and more!
